## Components Built

### `BoxInputLG` — `src/components/BoxInputLG/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/BoxInputs/Large" — 132px vertical card-style selection box
- **Props**: `value: string` (**required**), `name: string` (**required**), `label?: string` (bold header, 1–2 words), `description?: string` (body text), `modelValue?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Slots**: `#label` (override header text), `#description` (override body text)
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Layout**: `flex-direction: column` — header section (bold 16px) + divider + body section (14px regular)
- **Divider**: `box-shadow: 0 Npx 0 0 color` on `.box-input-lg__header` — thickens with state (1px → 2px → 3px) without any layout shift
- **Default border**: `--color-neutral-85` (#D4D7D9) — slightly darker than XS/SM/MD which use Neutral90
- **Outer border**: same `inset box-shadow` pattern as other BoxInput sizes (1px neutral-85 → 2px Primary50 → 3px Accessibility80)
- **`overflow: hidden`** on root clips the inner header shadow to the rounded corners
- **Stories**: Default, Hover, Selected, FocusSelected, Disabled, ConditionGroup, PaymentGroup, AllStates

### `BoxInputMD` — `src/components/BoxInputMD/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/BoxInputs/Medium" — 86px location/store selection box with rich label layout
- **Props**: `value: string` (**required**), `name: string` (**required**), `primaryLabel?: string` (bold, always shown), `secondaryLabel?: string`, `tertiaryLabel?: string`, `sideLabel?: string` (right-aligned, e.g. "4 mi"), `modelValue?: string`, `disabled?: boolean`
- **Slots**: `#secondary-icon` (optional 16×16 icon before secondary text — **only shown in default state**, CSS hides it on hover/selected/focus)
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Dimensions**: `height: 86px; padding: 24px; min-width: 126px; border-radius: --border-radius-md`
- **Typography**:
  - Primary: 16px bold / 24px line-height (`--font-weight-bold`)
  - Secondary/tertiary: 12px regular / 16px line-height / 0.2px letter-spacing
  - Side label: `--text-body-sm-size` (14px) / 22px line-height / right-aligned / `width: 77px`
- **States**: same inset box-shadow pattern as XS/SM (1px neutral → 2px green → 3px blue focus)
- **Icon hide behaviour**: `.box-input-md:hover`, `.box-input-md--selected`, and `:has(:focus-visible)` all set `.box-input-md__secondary-icon { display: none }`
- **Stories**: Default, Hover, Selected, FocusSelected, Disabled, WithSecondaryLabel, WithSecondarySelected, WithAllLines, NoSideLabel, LocationPicker (interactive), AllStates

