### `BoxInputXS` — `src/components/BoxInputXS/`
- **Figma**: "Inputs/BoxInputs/XS" — 48px selection box, pick-one-from-several (styled radio button)
- **Props**: `value: string` (**required** — this option's value), `name: string` (**required** — radio group name), `label?: string`, `modelValue?: string` (v-model), `disabled?: boolean`
- **Slots**: `#icon` (optional 16×16 SVG pinned to left edge at `left: 16px`, import with `?raw`)
- **Emits**: `update:modelValue: [value: string]`
- **Renders as**: `<label>` wrapping a visually-hidden `<input type="radio">` — fully accessible, native keyboard nav
- **States** (CSS `:has()` driven from native radio state):
  - Default: white bg, `inset 0 0 0 1px --color-neutral-90`
  - Hover: `--color-neutral-95` bg, 1px Neutral90
  - Selected: white bg, `inset 0 0 0 2px --color-base-primary-50`
  - Focus: `inset 0 0 0 3px --color-accessibility-80` (uses `:has(.box-input-xs__radio:focus-visible)`)
- **Dimensions**: `height: 48px; min-width: 175px; border-radius: --border-radius-md (8px); padding: 12px 16px`
- **Label typography**: `--text-body-lg-size` (16px) / `--text-body-lg-weight` (400) / `--text-body-lg-line-height` (1.5); centered
- **Usage pattern**: wrap multiple instances in a `<fieldset>` with shared `name` prop + single `v-model`
- **Stories**: Default, Hover, Selected, FocusSelected, Disabled, WithIcon, YesNoGroup, TimeSlotGroup, CategoryGroup, AllStates

### `VideoControlButton` — `src/components/VideoControlButton/`
- **Figma**: "Buttons/VideoControls" — 40×40px circular media control button
- **Props**: `ariaLabel: string` (**required**), `color?: 'dark' | 'light'` (default `'dark'`), `disabled?: boolean`, `href?: string`, `target?: string`
- **Slots**: `#icon` (24×24 SVG — import with `?raw`, wrap in `<span v-html="..." style="display:contents">`)
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]`
- **Themes**:
  - `dark`: Default `--color-neutral-20` (#313D47) → Hover/Press/Focus `--color-neutral-0` (#242C33); icon `--color-neutral-100` (white)
  - `light`: Default `rgba(255,255,255,0.6)` → Hover/Press/Focus `--color-neutral-100` (full white); icon `--color-neutral-0` (dark)
- **Focus border**: `border: 3px solid transparent` base + `box-sizing: border-box` → focus sets `border-color: --color-accessibility-80` (no layout shift)
- **Available media icons**: Play, Pause, Stop, Skip-Forward, Skip-Backward, Fullscreen, Exit-Fullscreen, Refresh (all in `icon/Style=Media, Detail=*, Icon=NA.svg`)
- **Stories**: DarkDefault, DarkHover, DarkPressed, DarkFocus, DarkDisabled, LightDefault, LightHover, LightFocus, AllStates, IconVariety

### `ArrowCircleButton` — `src/components/ArrowCircleButton/`
- **Figma**: "Buttons/ArrowCircle" — circular navigation/action button designed for image & carousel overlays
- **Props**: `ariaLabel: string` (**required**), `direction?: 'right' | 'left' | 'expand'` (default `'right'`), `size?: 'sm' | 'lg'` (default `'sm'`), `disabled?: boolean`, `href?: string`, `target?: string`
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]`
- **No icon slot** — icons are bundled internally based on `direction` prop (no need for consumers to import SVGs)
- **Theme is derived automatically** from `size` + `direction` — not a separate prop:
  - `sm` + `right|left` → "dark": `rgba(36,44,51, 0.3→0.6→0.75)` background, white icon (`--color-neutral-100`)
  - `sm` + `expand` → "green": Primary50→Primary40→Primary60 on hover/press, white icon
  - `lg` + `right|left` → "white": `rgba(255,255,255, 0.6)` → full white on hover/press, dark icon (`--color-neutral-0`)
- **Sizes**: sm = 32×32px circle; lg = 64×64px circle. Icon always 24×24px
- **Border**: `border: 3px solid transparent` (always reserves focus-ring space, `box-sizing: border-box`). Focus state sets `border-color: --color-accessibility-80` — no layout shift
- **Icons used**: `icon/Style=Arrows, Detail=Tail, Icon=Right.svg?raw`, `...Left.svg?raw`, `icon/Style=Media, Detail=Expand, Icon=NA.svg?raw`
- **Stories**: SmallRight, SmallLeft, SmallExpand (+ hover/focus variants), LargeRight, LargeLeft, AllVariants

### `SmallIconButton` — `src/components/SmallIconButton/`
- **Figma**: "IconButtons/Favorite" (32×32 toggle button)
- **Props**: `ariaLabel: string` (**required**), `selected?: boolean` (default `false`), `disabled?: boolean`
- **Slots**: `#icon` (24×24 SVG — full size inside 32px circle)
- **Emits**: `click: [event: MouseEvent]` — parent is responsible for toggling `selected`
- **Shape**: Fixed 32×32px circle, `background: --color-neutral-100` (white)
- **Key difference from other icon buttons**: white background + neutral grey border (NOT Accent blue)
- **Border**: real `border` (not box-shadow inset) — `box-sizing: border-box` keeps outer size exactly 32px regardless of border-width, so no layout shift. 1px Neutral90 default, 2px Neutral90 hover, 3px Accessibility80 focus
- **Icon colour via currentColor**:
  - Unselected: `--color-neutral-70` (grey)
  - Selected: `--color-base-primary-50` (green)
  - Hover + selected: `--color-base-primary-55` (lighter green)
  - Disabled: `--color-neutral-80` + `--opacity-level-medium`
- **Accessibility**: `ariaLabel` → `aria-label`; `selected` → `aria-pressed` (browser announces both)
- **Stories**: DefaultUnselected, DefaultSelected, HoverUnselected, HoverSelected, Focus, FocusSelected, Disabled, Interactive, AllStates, IconVariety

